  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  adult patients, 18-75 years of age;

          -  rheumatoid arthritis for &gt;=6 months;

          -  methotrexate for &gt;=12 weeks prior to day 1 (stable at 10-25mg/week for 8 weeks).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  history of, or current inflammatory joint disease or rheumatic autoimmune disease
             other than RA;

          -  concurrent treatment with any DMARD other than methotrexate;

          -  prior treatment with tocilizumab.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
